<p>As alternative to inorganic acids, tartaric acid along with H
 <sub>2</sub>O
 <sub>2</sub> gave the most promising results. Impressively, approximately 99% of Li, Co, Ni, and Mn were solubilized after 30 min at 70 °C [
 <xref rid="B208-materials-13-00801" ref-type="bibr">208</xref>]. The main reaction proposed by He et al. is:
 <disp-formula id="FD15-materials-13-00801">
  <label>(15)</label>
  <math id="mm16">
   <mrow>
    <mrow>
     <mn>2</mn>
     <mi>LiM</mi>
     <mrow>
      <mo>(</mo>
      <mrow>
       <mi>III</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mo>)</mo>
     </mrow>
     <msub>
      <mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi>
      <mrow>
       <mn>2</mn>
       <mrow>
        <mo>(</mo>
        <mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi>
        <mo>)</mo>
       </mrow>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <mo>+</mo>
     <mn>3</mn>
     <msub>
      <mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi>
      <mn>4</mn>
     </msub>
     <msub>
      <mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi>
      <mn>6</mn>
     </msub>
     <msub>
      <mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi>
      <mrow>
       <mn>6</mn>
       <mrow>
        <mo>(</mo>
        <mrow>
         <mi>aq</mi>
        </mrow>
        <mo>)</mo>
       </mrow>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <mo>+</mo>
     <msub>
      <mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi>
      <mn>2</mn>
     </msub>
     <msub>
      <mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi>
      <mrow>
       <mn>2</mn>
       <mrow>
        <mo>(</mo>
        <mrow>
         <mi>aq</mi>
        </mrow>
        <mo>)</mo>
       </mrow>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <mo>→</mo>
     <mn>2</mn>
     <mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi>
     <mrow>
      <mo>(</mo>
      <mrow>
       <mi>II</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mo>)</mo>
     </mrow>
     <msub>
      <mrow>
       <mrow>
        <mo>(</mo>
        <mrow>
         <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi>
          <mn>4</mn>
         </msub>
         <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi>
          <mn>4</mn>
         </msub>
         <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi>
          <mn>6</mn>
         </msub>
        </mrow>
        <mo>)</mo>
       </mrow>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
       <mrow>
        <mo>(</mo>
        <mrow>
         <mi>aq</mi>
        </mrow>
        <mo>)</mo>
       </mrow>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <mo>+</mo>
     <msub>
      <mrow>
       <mi>Li</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mn>2</mn>
     </msub>
     <msub>
      <mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi>
      <mn>4</mn>
     </msub>
     <msub>
      <mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi>
      <mn>4</mn>
